description:
The Maestros of TangoFest Palermo 2017 dance “Muñequita de París“ by Osvaldo Fresedo, sung by Héctor Pacheco in Palermo, Italy.

The Maestros are
Sofia Saborido and Pablo Inza
Maria Filali and Gianpiero Galdi
Maja Petrovic and Marko Miljevic
Lorena Tarantino and Giovanni Cocomero
